39:56.720 --> 39:58.040
[knocking]

40:01.960 --> 40:03.800
Mike.

40:03.920 --> 40:05.840
If I didn't know any better,I'd start to think you

40:05.960 --> 40:07.160
had a bit of a thing for me.

40:07.280 --> 40:08.960
You down this way I see a bit.

40:09.080 --> 40:11.760
You just can't take thingsat face value, can you?

40:11.880 --> 40:14.040
I was visiting the familyof my young friend, Falani.

40:14.160 --> 40:15.440
Seems to be the case.

40:15.560 --> 40:17.000
I take folks as I find them.

40:17.120 --> 40:19.920
Pigs or coconuts,
I'm not prejudiced.

40:20.040 --> 40:25.200
I'm off home, if you, uh,feel the need to follow me.

40:25.320 --> 40:33.120
[music playing]

40:33.240 --> 40:35.400
Sausage roll?

40:35.520 --> 40:36.960
Will it be dangerous?

40:37.080 --> 40:37.840
Not at all.

40:37.960 --> 40:47.360
[music playing]

40:47.480 --> 40:50.160
Have we heard from Carol?

40:50.280 --> 40:52.560
Safely installed
at a flat in Potsonby

40:52.680 --> 40:55.800
and loving it, apparently.

40:55.920 --> 40:59.280
And the insurance is
no longer a problem.

40:59.400 --> 41:01.400
How did you manage that?

41:01.520 --> 41:02.960
Sometimes working
in the second-hand

41:03.080 --> 41:06.440
business has its advantages.

41:06.560 --> 41:08.480
You are a marvel, sweetheart.

41:08.600 --> 41:09.720
You're not so bad yourself.

41:13.720 --> 41:16.120
What did you do?

41:16.240 --> 41:18.080
I just had a
little word to Talita

41:18.200 --> 41:20.080
and told her that Bilkey
was already married,

41:20.200 --> 41:22.520
and likes to pretend he's not.

41:22.640 --> 41:24.120
How did she take that?

41:24.240 --> 41:26.480
Not so well, at first.

41:26.600 --> 41:27.920
But then I pointed
out that there's

41:28.040 --> 41:32.400
this other bloke, single,doing well for himself,

41:32.520 --> 41:34.080
and loves island girls.

41:34.200 --> 41:37.960
They certainly go
after what they want.

41:38.080 --> 41:41.320
Excuse me.

41:41.440 --> 41:42.760
[chatter]

41:42.880 --> 41:44.200
[laughter]

41:44.320 --> 41:48.600
[music playing]

41:48.720 --> 41:50.760
He'll never get away now.

41:50.880 --> 41:51.640
At least he got a root.

41:55.640 --> 41:57.080
Poor old thing.

41:57.200 --> 42:00.560
Oh, well, at least
he's got his mammy.

42:00.680 --> 42:02.160
Hey, bro.

42:02.280 --> 42:05.440
Give me some skin, bro.

42:05.560 --> 42:06.320
Falani.

42:06.440 --> 42:07.760
Good to see see ya.

42:07.880 --> 42:09.080
Mr. Ted.

42:09.200 --> 42:12.000
What is this?

42:12.120 --> 42:13.480
Let's get this party happening.

